Plot:
-----
In this sequel to the Evil Dead films, a discount-store employee 
(Name's Ash. Housewares.) is time-warped to a medieval castle beset 
by monstrous forces. Initially mistaken for an enemy, he is soon revealed 
as the prophecised savior who can quest for the Necronomicon, a book which 
can dispel the evil. Unfortunately, he screws up the magic words while 
collecting the tome, and releases an army of skeletons, led by his own 
Deadite counterpart. What follows is a thrilling, yet tongue-in-cheek 
battle between Ash's 20th Century tactics and the minions of darkness. 

